    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels brand new! I have babied this ride since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and stayed on top of every single service. If you're looking for a perfect set of wheels without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
