    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that defies the typical expectations of a pre-owned car. This masterpiece has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains flawless and free of any rock chips or swirls. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery retains its original matte finish and factory scent, with absolutely no wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic feature, from the immersive sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule at authorized dealerships with all records organized and available. With exceptionally low mileage and a history of adult-driven care, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes both original keys, all manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
